{"id":14,"date":"2020-06-17T10:12:52","date_gmt":"2020-06-17T03:12:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/?page_id=14"},"modified":"2026-04-03T15:44:04","modified_gmt":"2026-04-03T08:44:04","slug":"homepage","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/","title":{"rendered":"homepage"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row_content_no_spaces&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; el_class=&#8221;header-banner&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; el_class=&#8221;t-bg-m&#8221;][vc_column_text el_class=&#8221;header-inner-text&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h1 class=\"header-text\">Solar Turbines<br \/>\nauthorized representative<\/h1>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1592370121871{padding-top: 35px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2>About Us<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thuong Thien Technologies Co. Ltd (TTT) has been in collaboration with Solar Turbines since last 20 years to provide Vietnam customers with the highest quality Gas Turbines, Generators, Compressors and Service Solutions within Oil &amp; Gas and Electricity Power Generation industries.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_raw_html][\/vc_raw_html][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;388&#8243; img_size=&#8221;large&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; full_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1592370154502{background-color: #f2f2f2 !important;}&#8221;][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Our Business<\/h2>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;62&#8243;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;3\/4&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1592535801018{border-left-width: 2px !important;padding-left: 30px !important;border-left-color: #374fa1 !important;border-left-style: solid !important;}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3>TTT activities in Vietnam<\/h3>\n<ul class=\"check-list\">\n<li>Coordinate, support Solar Turbines\/Customers on Sales and Operation activities.<\/li>\n<li>Organize events in Vietnam.<\/li>\n<li>Support customers in Solar Global events.<\/li>\n<li>Organize local trainings in Vietnam.<\/li>\n<li>Developing Power Generation business for industrial and commercial applications.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner gap=&#8221;10&#8243;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1592375161843{padding: 0px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<div class=\"ttt-info-box\">\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-338 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/oil-gas.jpg\" alt=\"Offshore\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/oil-gas.jpg 800w, https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/oil-gas-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/oil-gas-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/oil-gas-20x11.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<div class=\"ttt-icon-box\">\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-18 alignleft\" role=\"img\" src=\"https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/oil.svg\" alt=\"Oil icon\" width=\"39\" height=\"35\" \/><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"line-height: 25px; text-align: left;\">OIL &amp; GAS<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">From gas compression to remote power needs, Solar Turbines offers a wide range of Oil and Gas energy solutions that meet the highest of industry standards.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<style type=\"text\/css\" data-type=\"the7_shortcodes-inline-css\">#default-btn-a28a9c5214e052cb13ffbbe2f6a759e3.ico-right-side > i {\n  margin-right: 0px;\n  margin-left: 8px;\n}\n#default-btn-a28a9c5214e052cb13ffbbe2f6a759e3 > i {\n  margin-right: 8px;\n}\n#default-btn-a28a9c5214e052cb13ffbbe2f6a759e3 * {\n  vertical-align: middle;\n}\n<\/style><div class=\"btn-align-center\"><a href=\"\/oil-gas\/\" class=\"default-btn-shortcode dt-btn dt-btn-m link-hover-off full-width-btn \" id=\"default-btn-a28a9c5214e052cb13ffbbe2f6a759e3\" title=\"Oil & Gas\"><span>MORE<\/span><\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1592375154993{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<div class=\"ttt-info-box\">\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-339 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/power-generation.jpg\" alt=\"power-generation\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/power-generation.jpg 800w, https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/power-generation-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/power-generation-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/power-generation-20x11.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<div class=\"ttt-icon-box\">\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-22\" role=\"img\" src=\"https:\/\/thuongthien.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/power-generation.svg\" alt=\"power-generation icon\" width=\"35\" height=\"32\" \/><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"line-height: 25px; text-align: left;\">POWER GENERATION<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Solar Turbines offers a wide range of complete turbomachinery solutions designed to fit the energy and conservation needs of the Power Generation industry.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<style type=\"text\/css\" data-type=\"th